g.text: Sign up (school email or SSO) → verify email
Enter basics (major, grad year, location prefs)
Add skills, interests, desired job type
Swipe right = interested; left = pass; tap for details
Return to discovery or adjust filters
"It's a match!" modal with intro prompt
Send push/email notifications to both parties
Block or report user if needed
Propose or accept recruiter time slots
If ATS connected → create interview in Sys2
After event → swipe on companies or leave feedback
Weekly digest: matches, replies, suggested events
No reply after X days → send nudge or auto-close
